---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: How We Work
description: A simple, honest process from first email to launch and beyond. Discovery, quote, payment, intake, build, launch and ongoing support — mostly handled by email, around your schedule.
permalink: /how-we-work/
---
{% from "components/ui.njk" import icon, ctaBand, pageHero %}

{{ pageHero(
  "How we work",
  "A simple process, start to finish.",
  "From your first email to launch day and beyond, here's exactly what to expect. No lengthy meetings, no jargon, no surprises — most of it handled by email, around your schedule."
) }}

{# ============================================================= PROMISES #}
<section class="pb-4 sm:pb-8">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
      {% set promises = [
        { icon: "mail", title: "Mostly by email", text: "Reply whenever it suits you. A quick call is always optional, never required." },
        { icon: "clock-fast", title: "Clear timelines", text: "You'll know how long each step takes, and we keep you updated in plain English." },
        { icon: "shield", title: "No surprises", text: "Fixed quotes, honest advice and your website, domain and content always yours." }
      ] %}
      {% for p in promises %}
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-{{ loop.index0 }} flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6">
          <span class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-ink text-chartreuse-400">{{ icon(p.icon, "h-5 w-5") }}</span>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-ink">{{ p.title }}</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">{{ p.text }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================================= TIMELINE #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">The journey</span>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-display-sm">Seven steps to your new website.</h2>
      <p class="lede mx-auto mt-4">Each stage is designed to save you time and keep things simple.</p>
    </div>

    <ol class="relative mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl">
      {# Vertical connecting line #}
      <span class="absolute left-[1.4375rem] top-2 bottom-2 w-px bg-neutral-200 sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2" aria-hidden="true"></span>

      {% for step in journey %}
        <li class="reveal relative mb-10 last:mb-0 sm:mb-0 sm:grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-x-12 sm:py-6">
          {# Number marker #}
          <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 z-10 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-neutral-200 bg-white font-display text-sm font-semibold text-ink shadow-soft sm:left-1/2 sm:-translate-x-1/2">
            {{ step.step }}
          </span>

          {# Card — alternates side on desktop #}
          {% set isLeft = loop.index0 % 2 == 0 %}
          <div class="{{ 'sm:col-start-1 sm:text-right sm:pr-4' if isLeft else 'sm:col-start-2 sm:pl-4' }} pl-20 sm:pl-0">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 ease-gentle hover:shadow-soft">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">{{ step.title }}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">{{ step.description }}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

{# ============================================================= AFTER LAUNCH #}
<section class="section on-dark relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-24 top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-chartreuse-400/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="shell relative">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">And then?</span>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-display-sm">We don't disappear after launch.</h2>
        <p class="lede mt-4">
          The relationship really begins once your website is live. We stay on hand
          to make updates, answer questions and keep everything running smoothly —
          for the years ahead, not just the first week.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/website-packages/#support" class="btn-accent">See ongoing support {{ icon("arrow-right", "h-4 w-4") }}</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-outline">Start a conversation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <ul class="grid gap-4">
          {% set aftercare = [
            "Updates, changes and content edits handled for you",
            "Hosting, security and backups quietly taken care of",
            "A real person to email whenever you need us",
            "No long contracts — stay because it works"
          ] %}
          {% for a in aftercare %}
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-ink-800 p-5">
              <span class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-chartreuse-400 text-ink">{{ icon("check", "h-4 w-4") }}</span>
              <span class="text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-neutral-200">{{ a }}</span>
            </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{{ ctaBand() }}
